All visible things are Màyà. Mâyâ will vanish through the effect of knowledge
(jnâna). One must strive to get rid of Mâyâ, which devastates the mind; the
destruction of the mind (manas) means the annihilation of Mâyâ. Meditation is
the only way in which to dominate Mâyâ.
